public abstract class AbstractGraphicComponentSet<T extends GraphicComponent,​S extends AbstractGraphicComponentSet<T,​S>>
extends java.util.TreeSet<T>
implements java.lang.Cloneable, NotificationSet<T>
This class provides an ordered set containing graphic components. The components in this set are ordered ascendantly by their IDs.

Ming-Hsien Tsai
